name: Strands
description:
In the game Death Stranding by Hideo Kojima, the concept of a strand means you'll never play side by side with another player but anyone who plays the game has the ability to impact, influence, and even help you in your game. That's a lot like all of us on this HEN adventure. Thank you for all your support my community. Let's continue to build bridges and offer tools to help each other thrive. 

Code and Video Feedback representing all of us in the form of a looping strand.
